<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <title>Notice-bored</title>
    <style>
      body{
        background-color: aliceblue;
        color: navy;
      }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include ('partials/navbar.ejs') %>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1>About Our Noticeboard App</h1>
        <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
              <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                What is the purpose of this web application?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Our app serves as a public noticeboard where users can share and post announcements, particularly posters for upcoming events. It aims to facilitate community engagement by providing a centralized platform for event promotion and discussions.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                What key features and functionalities does the app offer?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                The app includes the following features:
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>Post Creation:</strong> Users can create posts and upload images.</li>
                  <li><strong>Post Editing:</strong> Users can edit the details of their posts.</li>
                  <li><strong>Post Deletion:</strong> Users can delete their posts.</li>
                  <li><strong>Post Retrieval:</strong> All created posts and their details are retrieved from the database and displayed when the page loads.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Who is the target audience for this app?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Our target audience includes individuals aged 18-45 who are interested in community events, local news, social events, and event planning. They need a simple interface for posting.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                What additional features are planned for future iterations?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Future iterations of the app may include:
                <ul>
                  <li>User Authentication: Implementing login functionality to ensure only authorized users can post and comment.</li>
                  <li>Search Functionality: Adding a search feature to help users find specific posts or events quickly.</li>
                  <li>Post Categories: Allowing users to categorize posts (e.g., Music Events, Sports Events) for better organization and filtering.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
</body>
</html>